<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>기업 목록</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .company-list {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .company-item {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .company-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .company-info {
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>기업 목록</h1>

<div class="company-list">
    <div class="company-item">
        <div class="company-name">잡코리아</div>
        <div class="company-info">기업 형태: 대기업 | 위치: 서울</div>
    </div>
    <div class="company-item">
        <div class="company-name">사람인</div>
        <div class="company-info">기업 형태: 중견기업 | 위치: 경기</div>
    </div>
    <div class="company-item">
        <div class="company-name">쿠팡</div>
        <div class="company-info">기업 형태: 대기업 | 위치: 서울</div>
    </div>
    <div class="company-item">
        <div class="company-name">배달의민족</div>
        <div class="company-info">기업 형태: 스타트업 | 위치: 서울</div>
    </div>
    <div class="company-item">
        <div class="company-name">카카오</div>
        <div class="company-info">기업 형태: 대기업 | 위치: 성남</div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
